To build a neural network from scratch, the essential ideas fall into a handful of core concepts
- CPU architecture
- Parallel Programming
- Tensor Math
- Autograd/backprop
- Training Mechanics

GPU & Cuda fundamentals
1. Cuda's execution model, 
- Threads
- - The smallest unit of work 
- Thread Blocks
- - Groups of threads that can synchronize and share memory
- Grid
- - All blocks launched for a kernel
- Kernels
- - GPU functions you laucn with <<<grid, block>>>

